  <Summary>The Creep scares up two all-new standalone stories in this star-studded anthology based on the hit Shudder TV series.

Francesco Francavilla (Night of the Ghoul, Detective Comics) and Lisa Francavilla welcome you to a barbershop where the locals share tales of their greatest kills, and the hunters can just as easily become prey.

Ariela Kristantina (Chain) and Jorge Corona (The Me You Love In The Dark) journey to a temple hidden within an island paradise, where many visit, but not everyone leaves.</Summary>
